# VHS documentation
# https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs#installation

Output jan_install.mp4

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 28
Set Width 1600
Set Height 900
Set TypingSpeed 140ms

Copy "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/finnoh/ti-student-agent-pack/main/install.sh"

Type "curl -sL "
Sleep 500ms
Paste
Sleep 500ms
Type " | bash"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 10s

Type "opencode"
Enter
Sleep 10s
